  "notes": [
    "This paper introduces a computational method for identifying genetic minimal intervention sets (gMIS) that extend beyond traditional synthetic lethality to include synthetic dosage lethality and tumor suppressor gene complexes",
    "The study uses integrated metabolic and regulatory network models to predict lethal genetic interactions in cancer cells",
    "Validation was performed using DepMap data and various databases including SLKB and TSGene2.0"
  ]
